Minimal Makeup Ft. Bold Lips
.
.
Enhancing your eyes with nude shades is the most minimal way of doing your eye makeup. I used two nude shades to enhance my crease and did not even need any eyeshadow on my entire lid for this look. I like to keep my eye look minimal when I want to go for a bold lip color. I hope you enjoy this look as much as I did. 
.
.
Ps- I have no idea why my left eye is red 🥲
